# Live Scraping Audit & Monitoring

## Phase 1: Database State Check
- [/] Query source registry — how many sources, which are active
- [ ] Query evidence records — how many records exist, when last scraped
- [ ] Identify data gaps

## Phase 2: Live Scraping Test
- [ ] Test scraping 3-5 sources manually via Firecrawl
- [ ] Test sub-page navigation and extraction
- [ ] Monitor extraction quality (prices found, accuracy)
- [ ] Test fallback chain (ScrapingDog, ScrapingAnt, Apify)

## Phase 3: Source Quality Assessment
- [ ] Grade each source: working / partial / broken
- [ ] Identify sources needing replacement
- [ ] Recommend new high-value sources

## Phase 4: Report & Recommendations
- [ ] Document findings in scraping audit report
